=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a8fa1dca5a739e29a7cc6813254267b6b51e99e","tid":275451,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T06:00:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔係一早收到風<br />\n邊有咁易拉到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用行李帶幾kg已經係最低莊手法<br />\n重有海路，陸路呢<br />\n偷運已經有千千萬萬種方法<br />\n<br />\n東南亞咁垃圾<br />\n有唔偷運既方法都唔出奇</blockquote><br />\n佢咁高調又放FB  唔比人檢舉先奇</blockquote><br />\n咁係條友柒啫 家陣運毒好興香咩周圍講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9c8945f19e46c896feaabb96c253e406603600f","tid":275451,"uid":31752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T06:09:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實有冇人真係被人插左毒品入行李賴野咁慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有人咁講過，查到話d野唔係自己</blockquote><br />\n係好驚依樣，無仇報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講真機場咁多CAM 如果比人放野入去應該會知道 <br />\n而且再查下身家背景目的地同埋出入境頻唔頻繁<br />\n有機會無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係有咁高技術神不知鬼不覺<br />\n去做機場小偷好過啦<br />\n<br />\n插毒品入人行李又擺唔多<br />\n比人周到就係藏毒<br />\n高風險低回報<br />\n<br />\n個個比人拉到都話插贓架啦<br />\n點插呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />擺係背囊最出面果格送比海關咩？<br />\n呢啲野只有自願，邊有咁多老屈<br />\n就算話好心幫人拎行李果啲都未必信得過"},{"pid":"3df14fb07a7725344fb061c3daca50f9dc68b3f3","tid":275451,"uid":70901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T06:10:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>利申，偷運過D火藥落香港，宜家先知驚，想知再講</blockquote><br />\n999 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></