,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T08:48:25.000Z","msg":"人在泰國  好想知有隻電打火機過唔過到關  而家好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d49363a35d5bb5aaf0e6095aace521b6d79b5a2","tid":275451,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T08:51:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dfc6bdf1e9c76e376de983acf019d62ace3427a0","tid":275451,"uid":33022,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T08:56:33.000Z","msg":"個三條傻閪真係抵死<br />\n係網上招人招到咁揚，諗都諗到自己幾多手啦<br />\n真係天真到想信係運木調？唔撚係嘛？分分鐘個大莊就係要搵x死鬼，交數俾政府。曬小小錢（市值一千萬，唔代表成本）叫佢地去死。可能同一日個大莊已經用第二種途徑去左一億貨啦。<br />\n人蠢真係唔係罪，無知先係最攞命"},{"pid":"4f6196bb147f8c0af6d4ece996a92999818fc6cf","tid":275451,"uid":33022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:03:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做都根本傻，擺明俾人交數。等班警察有功課交，唔洗發窮惡。</blockquote><br />\n咁又冇咁黑暗，交數就唔會攞咁大批貨出去啦，不過不排除放生明姐另有所圖</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一千萬好多咩 話唔定話背後已經有億億聲嘅貨過左過啦</blockquote><br />\n同意 特登放風話有一千萬貨 然後吸引注意力 跟住另一邊做億既貨</blockquote><br />\n記住，市值一千萬，唔係成本呀。大莊搵人做替死鬼，曬小小錢，又可以交數俾差佬，又可以聲東擊西，好似樓上巴打講成億貨用第種方法過左啦。係三個百痴唔識死"},{"pid":"d49f7438f99a4c7a1d78b873063a19f30d93074d","tid":275451,"uid":35581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:06:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>傻仔，去完巴西再去泰國，人地已經會特別留意</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同意，有可疑嘅概率相當高，想知某班飛機要檢查邊個行李根本有晒目標，一次半次可能走到，一年幾次來回，有親戚都唔會一年探幾次啦，除非查到你果邊有生意啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n尼樣真，出入境有時係要報目的<br />\n話旅遊又一年幾次真係當人傻仔</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">尼你老母</span>"},{"pid":"0be9b3622385d1dd356e33e938fe9791ec4ca368","tid":275451,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:18:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真心一問 其實去過好多地方見你係香港人都check得好hea甚至冇特別check過 早排去新加坡 入境同出境隨身行李直頭冇過x光機</blockquote><br />\n我帶左樽水新加坡返香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢照到有水<br />\n我明明記得到晒水<br />\n就大大聲話係吉樽<br />\n返黎先發覺真係成樽水滿晒"},{"pid":"b3cd2ef8fee0df919c89874b76ffb4f58b8af5d0","tid":275451,"uid":31384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:23:54.000Z","msg":"無鬼唔會死人"},{"pid":"02a5579cf296db1c291c09600224c11aa669017d","tid":275451,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:26:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無鬼唔會死人</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咪玩啦，我次次新年返大陸都俾香港海關截停，有次仲俾人的左入房搜身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f4ff1d2fa2dd0debca707043ce37fd728490082","tid":275451,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:32:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無鬼唔會死人</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咪玩啦，我次次新年返大陸都俾香港海關截停，有次仲俾人的左入房搜身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n海關：又係你條撚樣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98210bcf31976f87e11b1a804d0af1698ccae1fd","tid":275451,"uid":293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:34:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>無鬼唔會死人</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咪玩啦，我次次新年返大陸都俾香港海關截停，有次仲俾人的左入房搜身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n海關：又係你條撚樣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n陳生又係你呀"},{"pid":"e31536e6e6706613f813afbbabe303509ac4467d","tid":275451,"uid":11136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:35:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2663f3e56eee62d5dbf8b77f2c070eb31dab6411","tid":