kgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你，你一次半次，我係連續5年呀屌</blockquote><br />\n你的樣子如何"},{"pid":"341a025eaa621045ab0b4ca3d645d3c801372349","tid":275451,"uid":22560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:54:47.000Z","msg":"我有次真係喺曼谷機場等上機嗰陣買咗個木製裝飾品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef96147292f5f7e40705880b69cba7de39ec1c25","tid":275451,"uid":6267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T10:19:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>無鬼唔會死人</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咪玩啦，我次次新年返大陸都俾香港海關截停，有次仲俾人的左入房搜身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都試過同屋企人一齊過關都比人的左入房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你，你一次半次，我係連續5年呀屌</blockquote><br />\n你個樣衰格，咪俾人的！<br />\n<br />\n有朋友做海關，<br />\n<br />\n專捉d望副關員就移開視線或望住地下行既人，<br />\n<br />\n因為可疑，有時見條友一日見幾次，捉佢坐番個零鐘！"},{"pid":"a7c121a0a7d77e23ebc1e35d0fa0c91cde78adaf","tid":275451,"uid":70901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T11:16:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>利申，偷運過D火藥落香港，宜家先知驚，想知再講</blockquote><br />\n燙火藥？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n煙花爆竹仔"},{"pid":"fcc2e789745d68f8a76f65ada24ecf1b466655cb","tid":275451,"uid":70901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T11:18:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>傻仔，去完巴西再去泰國，人地已經會特別留意</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同意，有可疑嘅概率相當高，想知某班飛機要檢查邊個行李根本有晒目標，一次半次可能走到，一年幾次來回，有親戚都唔會一年探幾次啦，除非查到你果邊有生意啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n尼樣真，出入境有時係要報目的<br />\n話旅遊又一年幾次真係當人傻仔</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">尼你老母</span></blockquote><br />\n你老母尼"},{"pid":"71b746db2a3ab93ce262f9d3106f299be3cf71fb","tid":275451,"uid":2615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T12:18:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>傻仔，去完巴西再去泰國，人地已經會特別留意</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同意，有可疑嘅概率相當高，想知某班飛機要檢查邊個行李根本有晒目標，一次半次可能走到，一年幾次來回，有親戚都唔會一年探幾次啦，除非查到你果邊有生意啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n尼樣真，出入境有時係要報目的<br />\n話旅遊又一年幾次真係當人傻仔</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">尼你老母</span></blockquote><br />\n你老母尼</blockquote>"},{"pid":"5765a46b4f9c722c6fb47a6c3181d8d72dc27690","tid":275451,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T12:55:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>真心一問 其實去過好多地方見你係香港人都check得好hea甚至冇特別check過 早排去新加坡 入境同出境隨身行李直頭冇過x光機</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實只要扮到冇事有咩好驚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果你羅住 一千萬 毒品 可以扮到無事<br />\nOK....u win。<br />\n另外有樣叫閉路電視  由你 開始過關,其實已經開始有班人 做緊野, 唔好咁無知 比人呃。<br />\n以為過關 淨係過 x-ray 咁簡單。<br />\n同埋賭仔心態 以為成功一次 就越運越多。<br />\n有句說話叫 上多山多終遇虎。<br />\n同時某d年青人,諗下 點解每次 運少量 時就無事。<br />\n諗住運大量就出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實出事主要係線報+緝毒犬"},{"pid":"b9aae535b59e5290346e66e470af5a6922012ef8","tid":275451,"uid":88134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T13:06:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>無鬼唔會死人</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咪玩啦，我次次新年返大陸都俾香港海關截停，有次仲俾人的左入房搜身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都試過同屋企人一齊過關都比人的左入房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你，你一次半次，我係連續5年呀屌</blockquote><br />\n你的樣子如何</blockquote><br />\n賊眉賊眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4a77dded0528b9afcdbdc60f3a459e046c020d8","tid":275451,"uid":70689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T13:06:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockqu